  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nCORE Ep. 5 and Automata Pulls USDC from Marketplace\nThe Hologram News Network posted a video of the latest Star Atlas news.\nMetaverse Nomads #85\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their latest Star Atlas live stream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #70\nAephia published their latest Star Atlas newsletter.\nLanding Pads Graybox – STAR ATLAS\nGladiator posted a video analyzing some new images of Star Atlas development.\nStar Atlas Galactic Marketplace mishap allows ship NFTs to sell at insane discounts\nThe Hologram published an article about a mishap on the Star Atlas Marketplace.\nVSUS Solos Grayscale review – 4K STAR ATLAS Showroom\nGladiator posted a video review of the VSUS Solos Star Atlas ship.\nIs your system and Internet ready? STAR ATLAS\nGladiator posted a video of his thoughts on technology for Star Atlas.\nReview: The Club’s bot J33ves is your R4 supplier of last resort\nThe Hologram published an article about The Club’s bot J33ves.\nNext-Level Gaming: Unity + Web3!\nThe Hologram published an article about the Unity game engine.",
